![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/caca1d5c-2cb5-4b07-b1a3-a5e3a52d43df/ep317.jpg?format=original)

While The MCU gets all their ducks in a row for their Multiverse Saga, it's important to know that DC Comics INVENTED the Multiverse game! Not to be left in the dust, and just in time for the James Gun DCU reboot comes Justice League: Crisis on Infinite Earths Part 1, the animated adaption of one of DC's greatest stories. Join us as we talk about what this film is, could have been, and is trying to be in this multiverse-spanning review of the latest entry in DC Animation!

